# CROSS-CUTTING RULES (FE ↔ BE)

## When backend API changes

Do this checklist (in order):

1. Update OpenAPI (`docs/openapi/openapi.yaml` if used as source)
2. Update backend implementation + tests
3. Update frontend BFF proxy (/api/\*) if needed
4. Update frontend contracts (Zod) and clients
5. Update UI/PageModel usage + E2E/manual verification

## Breaking changes

- Propose compatibility strategy:
  - versioning OR migration plan OR fallback behavior
- Clearly list impacted routes and clients.
